DESCRIPTION:In partnership with the Kinsey Institute\,we present a convers
 ation with Katie Simon\, author ofTell Me What You Like: An Honest Discuss
 ion of Sex and Intimacy After Sexual Assault.ABOUT THE BOOK:Hopeful\, grou
 ndbreaking\, and anchored in true stories\, this much-needed book from sex
 uality journalist and fellow sexual assault survivor Katie Simon delves in
