UID:ai1ec-148607-95023@wfhb.org
DESCRIPTION:How do we instill a sense of responsibility to our environment
 ? This program dives into guiding philosophies of stewardship\, moral obli
 gation\, and ecological knowledge. [78 min. total runtime]There will be a 
 post-film Q&A with Earth Connection Film Festival directors Dr. Jessica Ei
 se (Indiana University) and Prof. Sarah Lasley (California State Polytechn
 ic University\, Humboldt). Following the screening\, there will be a plant
  propagation party in the lower lobby from 3-3:45pm.
LOCATION:IU Cinema\, 1213 E. 7th Street\, Bloomington (on the North end of
  the IU Auditorium)
