  InterdependenceHow do we view our interdependent relationship to Earth? T
 his program zooms in on our reliance on Earth and its resources for our li
 ves and well-being. [76 min. total runtime]There will be a Q&A with The Ol
 d Bear filmmaker Julie Busse following this screening.
