DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260611T213000
UID:ai1ec-140559-90754@wfhb.org
DESCRIPTION:Some revolutions happen in the streets. Others in the lab.Kat 
 and Henry\, two graduate students from opposing scientific disciplines\, a
 re forced to share a lab at Columbia University in 1968. Amidst interperso
 nal differences\, a campus devolving into political chaos\, and the uncert
 ainty and turmoil of the outside world\, they each discover what it’s li
 ke to be thrown into someone else’s orbit. By Jacqueline Bircher\, playw
 right of Constellation’s hit production of Webster’s B!+@#. Recommende
 d for ages 13+.Event Website:https://seeconstellation.org/mainstage/anothe
 r-revolution/
LOCATION:Constellation Playhouse\,107 W 9th St\, Bloomington
URL:https://wfhb.org/event/another-revolution-presented-by-constellation-s
 tage-screen/?instance_id=90754
X-SOURCE:WFHB Community Calendar
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Design & Donuts
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260612T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260612T100000
UID:ai1ec-148247-94842@wfhb.org
DESCRIPTION:A friendly environment to discuss any design-related challenge
 s\, questions\, and ideas. Learn from others as we talk about tools\, stra
 tegies\, and handy resources. And of course donuts! (Along with fruit\, te
 a & coffee.)Whether you’re a design pro or simply dabble in Canva — if
  you have any interest in design or just want to learn more\, you’re wel
 come!Facilitated by Catherine Pearce & Dave Martin.Free & open to the comm
 unity. No registration required.Repeats the second Friday of every month\,
  9:00–10:00 AM.Hosted at The Mill — dimensionmill.org
LOCATION:The Mill\, 642 N Madison St\, Bloomington
URL:https://wfhb.org/event/design-donuts/?instance_id=94842
X-SOURCE:WFHB Community Calendar
END:VEVENT
